      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FANTASTIC ZOHAN (1) racing well without winning, placing at his last four runs. Last start finished 3rd in a Mix 3/4 on March 13 over 510m at Sale behind DR. AZURE beaten 7 lengths (29.06). Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Racing well and deserves a win. HARD ROW (5) was in winning form two back (25.82) at this track but ran below best last time at Geelong, finishing 7th. Form here at the trip sound including two wins. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. Must be included in calculations. DESPICABLE ANDY (2) beaten last start over the 460m at Geelong but finished in the minors in a useful 25.89. Expecting another bold showing. DR. AZURE (3) boasts a solid strike-rate over this trip.",
